com.cmput301.cs.project.activities

Class ClaimListActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • ListActivity
      • com.cmput301.cs.project.activities.ClaimListActivity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TagsChangedListener, TagSelectorListener

    public class ClaimListActivity
extends ListActivity
implements TagsChangedListener, TagSelectorListener
    Is the activity that launches at start of app.

    An activity that shows a list of Claims.

    Redirects to LoginActivity if no user is found. Has menu buttons that allow the creation of new claims via EditClaimActivity and for the TagManagerActivity.

    If a claim item is clicked ClaimViewActivity is called for that claim.

    Finally there are tabs at the top of the activity that allow the user to switch between approver and claimant. Claimant shows only claims for the current user and Approver shows a list of the claims for every user EXCEPT the current user.

    If a tag is renamed or deleted the onTagRename and onTagResume methods, respectively, will reload the list of claims.

    Author:
    rozsa, jbenson
